The Khan looked over a ridge at the ongoing battle. There were only 
two defending units, presumably the Tripredacus, but their base 
defenses gave them an even edge with the numerous attackers.

Vlad: Your codename will be Drake for this battle, warrior. We go in 
and we pick one target each, then move on when its down. Skill, Drake!

He picked up a lot of speed and picked a target... Waspinator!
